  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Surgical outcome of entropion associated with Down's syndrome was evaluated. Grading scale of
      superficial punctate keratopathy and score of wearing glasses to correct refractive errors
      were measured.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
